{{see|Superman}}
==English==

===Noun===
'''superman'''  (''plural:'' '''[[supermen]]''')
# A superior type of man, described by Nietzche as the next step in human evolution; [[übermensch]].

2. A popular fictional character named Kael from the planet Krypton who, while under Earth's yellow sun, has "super" powers (e.g., the ability to fly, super strength, tough skin, heat vision, and extreme speed). 
